---
// 關於頁面 — 介紹這個網站和經營者
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Work Anywhere"
  description="Learn about Work Anywhere — your guide to remote work, digital nomad lifestyle, and location-independent living."
>
  <main>
    <h1>About Work Anywhere</h1>

    <p>
      <strong>Work Anywhere</strong> is a curated resource for anyone who wants to work from anywhere.
    </p>

    <p>
      Whether you're a seasoned digital nomad bouncing between coworking spaces in Bali
      and Lisbon, or you're just starting to explore the idea of remote work — this site
      is built for you.
    </p>

    <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>City Guides</strong> — Honest breakdowns of the best (and most overrated) remote work destinations. Cost of living, internet speed, visa info, and real community vibes.</li>
      <li><strong>Tool Reviews</strong> — Side-by-side comparisons of the software and gear that make remote work possible.</li>
      <li><strong>Job Hunting</strong> — Where to find legitimate remote jobs, how to stand out, and which platforms are worth your time.</li>
      <li><strong>Lifestyle</strong> — Productivity, mental health, community building, and the stuff nobody tells you about location-independent living.</li>
      <li><strong>Finance & Taxes</strong> — Banking across borders, digital nomad taxes, and managing money when your "home" changes every few months.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why This Site Exists</h2>

    <p>
      The internet is full of generic "top 10 digital nomad cities" listicles written by people
      who've never set foot in those places. We do the research, talk to real nomads, and
      compile information you can actually use to make decisions.
    </p>

    <p>
      No fluff. No AI-generated filler. Just useful, well-researched guides for people who
      want to build a life that isn't tied to a single zip code.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <p>
      Have a question, suggestion, or want to contribute? <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a>.
    </p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  main {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2em 1.5em 4em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-top: 2em;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.2em;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.6em;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
